snippet.title: Johnny Depp Stands up to Malignant Narcissist Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Sometimes we have to fight the most malignant narcs.
As I reference and read from the latest court document in Johnny Depp's lawsuit against Amber Heard, you are all going to see just how completely vile and monstrous this woman is.
Hopefully this should put everything in perspective and Johnny Depp can TRULY get his life back.
Here are links from other sources I also reference in this video.  Thank you all for watching and Keep Truth Alive!


 DEADLINE: Johnny Depp sues Amber Heard for 50 Million
https://deadline.com/2019/03/johnny-depp-amber-heard-defamation-lawsuit-abuse-claims-1202568137/
30-Page Document details—Adam Waldman, Johnny Depp’s Lawyer
https://pmcdeadline2.files.wordpress.com/2019/03/depp-heard-virginia-suit.pdf
“Johnny Depp’s Statement of Truth”—My video reading Depp’s Witness Statement for the Sun Lawsuit complete with links in the description box
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6NMVDUNjUA&t=1152s
Amber Heard’s Letter to “silent sisters” in Porter Magazine
https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amber-heard-essay-domestic-abuse-letter-955685
Jambernews—ANDY STERIS, Creator
https://jambernews.wordpress.com/tag/johnny-depp/
Link to my Retweet of Bette White’s Thread on Twitter
https://twitter.com/FantasyWeavers/status/1103451175263879169
Joe Rogan Experience Podcast—Asia Argento Controversy-where he says women can’t be predators like men can. 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DKuJdTnQ0kA
Link to my tweet with Amber Heard’s mugshot from when she was young, and a record of an arrest for driving while her license was suspended.  They are mysteriously gone from her records now.  Hmmm…
https://twitter.com/FantasyWeavers/status/1085697452680855552
Johnny Depp an “Emotional Mess” since divorce filing by Amber Heard and allegations—PeopleMagazine
https://people.com/movies/johnny-depp-amber-heard-divorce-actor-has-been-an-emotional-mess/
Amber Heard Pleads Guilty to Falsifying Document in Dog-smuggling trial in Australia
https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2016/04/18/amber-heard-pleads-guilty-australian-dog-smuggling/83174558/
Amber Heard’s arrest for hitting Tasya Van Ree—Arresting Officer a Lesbian despite “homophobia” accusations by Heard 
https://www.tmz.com/2016/06/09/officer-beverly-leonard-arrested-amber-heard/
Doug Stanhope—“Johnny Depp is being Blackmailed by Amber Heard…” –THE WRAP
https://www.thewrap.com/johnny-depp-is-being-blackmailed-by-amber-heard-heres-how-i-know-guest-column/
Dr. Fuck You Blog
